PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 32 - which (a) DECLARES the viral epidemic of Infectious Salmon Anaemia which caused extensive damage to the NEW BRUNSWICK salmon aquaculture industry in 1996 and 1997, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
